skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: grub guru
des:
We all know it might be hard to get the ball rolling when it comes to choosing what to eat. Grub Guru will name random restaurants for you, helping you narrow down your decision! 

Later on, more functionality will be added including smarter choices based off of your location, previous "thumbs ups", and more.

No hardware or account requirements are needed. Grub on!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
